(14, 14, 'category', 'Defer parsing of JavaScript\r\n\r\nIn order to load a page, the browser must parse the contents of all \r\ntags, which adds additional time to the page load. By minimizing the amount of\r\n\r\nJavaScript needed to render the page, and deferring parsing of unneeded\r\nJavaScript until it needs to be executed, you can reduce the initial load time of\r\nyour page.\r\n\r\nHow does your site score on this recommendation?', 8, 1),
